      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJESTIC SUMMER (6) led last time out and saluted at this track over 2230m, getting home by 5.5 metres. That followed an encouraging minor placing at this track the start prior. Stepping up a level this time but she is capable of another big performance. DAISY BOUCHEA (7) won at this track two runs ago but couldn't repeat the dose at her latest appearance over 1800m at this track, beaten 3 metres. Ideally placed and is sure to be there at the finish. FEEL THE MOMENT (5) didn't do a bad job when fifth over 1800m at this track last time out. Has top-three claims. STAR OF PATRICK (4) found form and finished in the money two runs ago then came back to earth when he broke and finished tenth last start over 1800m at this track, coming home 35 metres from the winner. Finds a nice race and can make up for that last start mishap.",
